Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.12,0:00:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Once upon a time,\Nin a magical land of Equestria...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...there were two regal sisters\Nwho ruled together...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,...and created harmony for all the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,To do this, the eldest used her unicorn\Npowers to raise the sun at dawn...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...the younger brought out\Nthe moon to begin the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, the two sisters maintained balance\Nfor their kingdom and their subjects:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.87,0:00:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All the different types of ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But as time went on,\Nthe younger sister became resentful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The ponies relished and played in the day\Nher elder sister brought forth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.09,0:00:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...but shunned and slept\Nthrough her beautiful night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.78,0:00:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,One fateful day, the younger unicorn refused\Nto lower the moon to make way for the dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The elder sister tried to reason with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.97,0:00:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...but the bitterness in the young one's heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.18,0:00:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...had transformed her into a\Nwicked mare of darkness:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.42,0:00:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nightmare Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.80,0:01:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,She vowed that she would shroud\Nthe land in eternal night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Reluctantly, the elder sister harnessed\Nthe most powerful magic known to ponydom:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.49,0:01:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Elements of Harmony!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.11,0:01:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Using the magic of the Elements of Harmony,\Nshe defeated her younger sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.60,0:01:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...and banished her permanently in the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.73,0:01:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The elder sister took on responsibility\Nfor both sun and moon....
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.90,0:01:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...and harmony has been maintained\Nin Equestria for generations since.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... Elements of Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I've heard of those before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.10,0:01:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But where?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.63,0:01:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Little Pony, My Little Pony...\NAaaaah...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.32,0:01:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Little Pony{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.68,0:01:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I used to wonder what friendship could be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Little Pony{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until you all shared its magic with me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.27,0:01:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Big adventure\NTons of fun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A beautiful heart\NFaithful and strong{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sharing kindness\NIt's an easy feat{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.16,0:02:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And magic makes it all complete!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.29,0:02:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have My Little Pony...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.62,0:02:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you know you are my very best friends?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.90,0:02:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Moondancer is having a little get-together\Nin the west castle courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna come?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.61,0:02:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry girls. I got a lot\Nof studying to catch up on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that pony do anything except study?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.12,0:02:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she's more interested\Nin books than friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I've heard of the Elements of Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike! Spike!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:02:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:02:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, find me that old copy of\N"Predictions and prophecies".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.23,0:03:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it was a gift for Moondancer, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.07,0:03:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spike. You know we don't\Nhave time for that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.32,0:03:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're on a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No... no, no, no no no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,SPIKE!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Elements... elements, e e e... Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Elements of Harmony... See: Mare in the Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mare in the Moon?\NBut that's just an old ponies' tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.01,0:03:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mare... mare... AHA!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.11,0:03:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Mare in the Moon - myth\Nfrom olden pony times..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:03:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"...a powerful pony, who\Nwanted to rule Equestria..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:03:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"...defeated by the Elements of Harmony\Nand imprisoned in the moon."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:04:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Legend has it that on the longest\Nday of the thousandth year..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"...the stars will aid in her escape and\Nshe will bring about nighttime eternal."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike! Do you know what this means?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.98,0:04:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a note, please. To the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.44,0:04:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okie dokie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,"My dearest teacher. My continuing studies\Nof pony magic have led me to discover..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-"...that we're on the precipice of disaster."\N-Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Preci... preci...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,-Threshold.\N-Threee...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Brink?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That something really bad is about to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,"For you see, the mythical Mare in\Nthe Moon is in fact Nightmare Moon..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"...and she's about to return to Equestria\Nand bring with her eternal night."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"Something must be done to make sure this\Nterrible prophecy does not come true."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"I await your quick response.\NYour faithful student, Twilight Sparkle."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.87,0:05:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight. Sparkle. Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.50,0:05:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Send it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,-Now?\N-Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia is a little busy getting\Nready for the Summer Sun Celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.19,0:05:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's, like, the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just it, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The day after tomorrow is the thousandth\Nyear of the Summer Sun Celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's imperative that\Nthe Princess is told right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Impera... impera...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Important!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There! It's on its way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.41,0:05:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wouldn't hold your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm not worried, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess trusts me completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In all the years she's been my mentor,\Nshe's never once doubted me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I knew she would wanna\Ntake immediate action.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"My dearest, most faithful student, Twilight."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:06:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"You know that I value your diligence\Nand that I trust you completely."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.18,0:06:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"But you simply must stop\Nreading those dusty old books."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"My Dear Twilight. There is more to\Na young pony's life than studying."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.95,0:06:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"So I'm sending you\Nto supervise the preparations..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"...for the Summer Sun Celebration in\Nthis year's location, Ponyville."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"And I have an even more essential\Ntask for you to complete."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"Make some friends!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Look on the bright side, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.37,0:06:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess arranged for you to stay in a library.\NDoesn't that make you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes it does. You know why?\NBecause I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll check on the preparations\Nas fast as I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.65,0:06:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...then get to the library and find\Nsome proof of Nightmare Moon's return.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then when will you make friends,\Nlike the Princess said?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She said to check on preparations.\NI am her student and I'll do my royal duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But the fate of Equestria does\Nnot rest on me making friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the ponies in Ponyville have\Ninteresting things to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight. Just try.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.10,0:07:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was interesting, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer Sun Celebration:\NOfficial Overseer's Checklist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Number 1: Banquet preparations.\NSweet Apple Acres.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,YEEHAW!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get this over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.32,0:07:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon. My name is Twilight Sparkle...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, howdy-do, miss Twilight?\NA pleasure makin' your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Applejack. We here at Sweet Apple Acres\Nsure do like makin' new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Friends? Actually... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what can I do you for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I am in fact here to supervise\Npreparations for the Summer Sun Celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're in charge of the food?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We sure as sugar are.\NWould you care to sample some?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as it doesn't take too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Soup's on, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.13,0:08:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, why don't I introduce\Ny'all to the Apple family?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.24,0:08:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but I really need to hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This here's Apple Fritter,\NApple Bumpkin, Red Gala...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...Red Delicious, Golden Delicious, Caramel\NApple, Apple Strudel, Apple Tart, Baked Apple,\NApple Brioche, Apple Cinnamon Crisp...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Macintosh, Apple Bloom\Naaaand Granny Smith.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Up and at 'em Granny Smith. We got guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...? Soup's on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm up, here I come, I'm comin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, I'd say they're already part of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:09:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Well, I can see the food situation\Nis handled, so we'll be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you gonna to stay for brunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we have an awful lot to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Food's all taken care of. Next is weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... I ate too much pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There's supposed to be a pegasus pony\Nnamed Rainbow Dash clearing the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she's not doing a very good job, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.41,0:09:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops. I guess I overdid it.\NUm... uh, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.44,0:10:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My very own patented Rain-Blow Dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No no, don't thank me. You're quite welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me guess, you're Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The one and only!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? You heard of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you're supposed\Nto be keeping the sky clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Twilight Sparkle and the Princess\Nsent me to check on the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. That'll be a snap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it in a jiffy. Just as soon\Nas I'm done practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Practicing for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The Wonderbolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna perform at\Nthe celebration tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm gonna show 'em my stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-*The* Wonderbolts?\N-Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.86,0:10:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The most talented flyers in all of Equestria?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:10:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:10:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Pfft... Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.37,0:11:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd never accept a pegasus who can't\Neven keep the sky clear for one measly day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.91,0:11:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. I could clear the sky in ten seconds flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Loop-de-loop around and WHAM!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.48,0:11:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd I say. Ten. Seconds. Flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never leave Ponyville hanging.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.97,0:11:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You should see the look on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a laugh, Twilight Sparkle.\NI can't wait to hang out some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. She's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! It's kinda pretty once you get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Decorations. Beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The decor's coming along nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:12:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This oughta be quick.\NI'll be at the library in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the decor. Her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no... Oh my goodness no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How are my spines? Are they straight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.95,0:12:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.05,0:12:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a moment, please.\NI'm in the zone as it were.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes! Sparkle always does\Nthe trick, does it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, Rarity, you are a talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... um, how can I help youuuuaAARGH!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my stars, darling! What ever\Nhappened to your coiffure?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean my mane? Well, it's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.02,0:12:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just here to check on the decorations\Nand then I'll be out of your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.03,0:12:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of MY hair? What about YOUR hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.50,0:12:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Where are we going? HELP!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Too green. Too yellow. Too puffy.\NNot puffy enough. Too frilly. Too shiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:13:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go on, my dear.\NYou were telling me where you're from.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've... urgh... been... sent...\Nfrom... Canterlot... to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.26,0:13:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Canterlot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I am so envious. The glamor, the sophistication.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always dreamed of living there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to hear all about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We are gonna be the best of friends, you and I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Emerald?! What was I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.90,0:13:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me get you some rubies!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick! Before she decides\Nto dye my coat a new color.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.28,0:13:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't she wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus, Casanova. What's next on the list?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Music. It's the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my. Um... Stop, please, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.05,0:14:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir. I mean, no offense.\NBut your rhythm is just a teeny, tiny bit off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now follow me, please. A one.\NA two. A one-two-three...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my. I'm so sorry.\NI didn't mean to frighten your birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just here to check up on the music\Nand it's sounding beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Twilight Sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I'm Fluttershy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't quite catch that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, um, it looks like your birds are back,\Nso I guess everything's in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooookay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that was easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.86,0:15:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A BABY DRAGON!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've never seen a baby dragon before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.21,0:15:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well well well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.42,0:15:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, he talks.\NI didn't know dragons could talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.28,0:15:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just so incredibly wonderful. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't even know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in that case we better be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait! What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Spike. I'm Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.30,0:15:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! A talking dragon!\NAnd what do dragons talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-Well, what do you wanna know?\N-Absolutely everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I started out as a cute\Nlittle purple-and-green egg...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...and that's the story of my whole entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, up until today.\NDo you wanna hear about today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:16:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry! How did we get here so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where I'm staying while in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.13,0:16:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-And my poor baby dragon needs his sleep.\N-No, I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Awww, wook at that. He's so sweepy, he\Ncan't even keep his wittle bawance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing. You simply must get into bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes yes. We'll get right on that.\NWell, goodnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.02,0:16:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Rude much?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.70,0:16:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Spike. But I have to convince the\NPrincess that Nightmare Moon is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...and we're running out of time!\NI just need to be alone, so I can study...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...without a bunch of crazy ponies\Ntrying to make friends all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now where's the light?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,SURPRISE!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi! I'm Pinkie Pie and I threw\Nthis party just for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you surprised, were you, were you?\NHuh huh huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Very surprised.\NLibraries are supposed to be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's silly! What kind of welcome\Nparty would this be if it were quiet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, DUH! BORING!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.42,0:17:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,YouseeIsawyouwhenyoufirstgothereremember?\NYouwereallhelloandIwasallGASPremember?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,YouseeIneversawyoubeforeandifInever\Nsawyoubeforethatmeansyourenew!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause I know everypony,\Nand I mean everypony in Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Andifyourenewthenyouhaventmetanyoneyetandifyou\Nhaventmetanyoneyetyoumustnothaveanyfriends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.20,0:17:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Andifyoudonthaveanyfriendsthenyoumustbelonely\NandthatmademesosadandIhadanideaandthatswhyIGASP!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Illjustthrowagreatbigginormoussuperduperspectacular\NwelcomepartyandinviteeveryoneinPonyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,See? And now you have lots and lots of friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, sugar cube?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Awww, she's so happy, she's crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.02,0:17:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Twilight! Pinkie Pie started\NPin the Tail on the Pony. Wanna play?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:18:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No! All the ponies in this town are CRAZY!\NDo you know what time it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the eve of the Summer Sun Celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony has to stay up or they'll\Nmiss the Princess raise the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You really should lighten up Twilight.\NIt's a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I thought I'd have time to learn\Nmore about the Elements of Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But, silly me, all this ridiculous\Nfriendmaking has kept me from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Legend has it that in the longest day\Nof the thousandth year..."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"...the stars will aid in her escape and\Nshe will bring about everlasting night."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.35,0:18:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope the Princess was right.\NI hope it really is just an old pony tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight!\NIt's time to watch the sun rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.38,0:18:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,AreyouexcitedcauseImexcited\NIveneverbeensoexcitedwell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.95,0:18:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...exceptforthattimethatIsawyouwalking\NintothistownandIwentGASP
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I mean, really, who can top that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Fillies and gentlecolts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As mayor of Ponyville,\Nit is my great pleasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...to announce the beginning\Nof the Summer Sun Celebration!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In just a few moments our town will\Nwitness the magic of the sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And celebrate this, the longest day of the year!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And now it is my great honor to\Nintroduce to you the ruler of our land.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.55,0:19:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The very pony, who gives us the sun\Nand the moon each and every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The good, the wise, the bringer\Nof harmony to all of Equestria...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,...Princess Celestia!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.82,0:19:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Remain calm, everypony.\NThere must be a reasonable explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.43,0:19:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I love guessing games! Is she hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.81,0:20:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Nightmare Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my beloved subjects!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.87,0:20:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so long since I've seen your\Nprecious little sun-loving faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do with our Princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.73,0:20:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa there, Nelly...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, am I not royal enough for you?\NDon't you know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,More guessing games!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.53,0:20:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Pokey Smokes!\NHow about Queen Meanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Black Snooty, Black Snooty...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.89,0:20:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Does my crown no longer count now that\NI have been imprisoned for a thousand years?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you not recall the legend?\NDid you not see the signs?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I did! And I know who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Mare in the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:20:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nightmare Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.70,0:21:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well well well. Somepony who remembers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.21,0:21:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you also know why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.27,0:21:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here to... to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.84,0:21:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember this day, little ponies,\Nfor it was your last.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,From this moment forth...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.15,0:21:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,THE NIGHT WILL LAST FOREVER!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.59,0:21:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Synced by Nathan2000\Nhttp://mlp.wikia.com/wiki/User:Nathan2000
